aking%20a%20company%20public%2C%20and%20Digital%20Offering%20was%20able%20to%20enumerate%20its%20vision.%20%26quot%3BWe%20felt%20that%20it%20would%20really%20create%20visibility%20for%20the%20company%20beyond%20just%20raising%20money%2C%20but%20actually%20creating%20visibility%20for%20the%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElenowitz%20spearheaded%20the%20Newsmax%20transaction%20alongside%20Gordon%20McBean%2C%20the%20bank's%20cofounder%20and%20chairman%20and%20a%20veteran%20of%20Lehman%20Brothers%20and%20Wells%20Fargo%3B%20and%20Mike%20Boswell%2C%20an%20MD%20who%20also%20has%20business%20interests%20in%20the%20defense%20sector%20and%20blockchain%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20Offering%20saw%20Newsmax%20as%20the%20right%20candidate%20for%20a%20Regulation%20A%2B%20offering%20because%20of%20its%20consumer%20appeal.%20Whereas%20a%20traditional%20IPO%20prioritizes%20large%20institutional%20investors%2C%20a%20Reg%20A%20offering%20lets%20companies%20raise%20money%20from%20accredited%20and%20non-accredited%20investors%2C%20including%20mom-and-pop%20retail%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20buying%2C%20as%20an%20institution%2C%20a%20million%20dollars%20and%20really%20being%20concerned%2C%20these%20are%20investors%20that%20are%20buying%20%24500%2C%20%241000%26quot%3B%20worth%20of%20equity%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20gives%20management%20the%20time%20to%20stop%20worrying%20about%20their%20stock%20price%20and%20focus%20on%20growth%20their%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20past%2048%20hours%20have%20been%20a%20rush%20for%20Elenowitz.%20The%20phones%20have%20been%20ringing%20off%20the%20hook%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20rejoiced%20over%20a%20celebratory%20dinner%2C%20and%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20are%20departing%20to%20Paris%20this%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20highlight%20was%20ringing%20the%20trading%20bell%20at%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20on%20Monday.%20An%20exchange%20official%20handed%20Elenowitz%20a%2