ms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%2C%2033%2C%20teaches%20Pilates%20in%20Miami%20Beach%2C%20where%20she%20and%20her%20mother%20live%20in%20the%20same%20waterfront%20apartment%20building.%20In%20her%20previous%20career%2C%20she%20founded%20Frank%2C%20a%20website%20that%20helped%20students%20fill%20out%20their%20federal%20financial%20aid%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20found%20on%20Friday%20that%20Javice%20used%20fake%20data%20to%20trick%20JPMorgan%2C%20the%20country's%20largest%20bank%2C%20into%20believing%20her%20website%20had%20gathered%20the%20names%20and%20other%20personal%20data%20of%20more%20than%204%20million%20students.%20The%20bank%20had%20hoped%20to%20market%20checking%20accounts%20and%20credit%20cards%20to%20these%20students%2C%20but%20later%20found%20that%20Javice%20had%20data%20for%20fewer%20than%20300%2C000%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge's%20ankle%20monitor%20decision%20on%20Tuesday%20followed%20some%2090%20minutes%20of%20arguments%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20Manhattan%20%E2%80%94%20complete%20with%20court%20exhibits%20showing%20Javice%20teaching%20Pilates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20arguing%20against%20the%20ankle%20monitor%2C%20Javice's%20lawyer%2C%20Ron%20Sullivan%2C%20told%20the%20judge%20that%20Javice%20has%20never%20missed%20a%20day%20of%20court%20and%20is%20not%20a%20flight%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWearing%20the%20bulky%20device%20once%20again%20%E2%80%94%20as%20she%20had%20for%20several%20weeks%20before%20a%20November%20decision%20granting%20its%20removal%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20a%20severe%20impediment%20to%20her%20career%20as%20a%20Pilates%20instructor%2C%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20have%20your%20legs%20in%20the%20air%20and%20the%20monitor%20going%20up%20and%20down%20on%20your%20leg%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20a%20significant%20encumbrance%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20told%20the%20judge.%20The%20lawyer%20held%20both%20arms%20aloft%20and%20waved%20them%20back%20and%20forth%20to%20demonstrate%20as%20he%