nger%20ties.%20He%20began%20his%20speech%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20tough%2C%20as%20modern%20nation%20states%2C%20we%20have%20had%20only%2075%20years%20of%20formal%20ties%2C%20India%20and%20China%20have%20shared%20cultural%20and%20civilizational%20ties%20and%20people-to-people%20contacts%20going%20back%20millenia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20spoke%20about%20significant%20%26quot%3Bcontributions%20by%20personalities%20such%20as%20Bodhidharma%2C%20Kumarajiva%2C%20Xuanzang%2C%20and%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%26quot%3B%20towards%20fostering%20historical%20India-China%20relations.%20He%20added%20that%20%26quot%3BOur%20two%20civilizations%20have%2C%20each%20in%20their%20own%20unique%20way%2C%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20shaping%20human%20history.%20This%20holds%20a%20lesson%20for%20contemporary%20ties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20second%20lesson%2C%20Mr%20Misri%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20India-China%20relations%20have%20gone%20through%20a%20difficult%20phase.%20But%20largely%2C%20due%20to%20the%20guidance%20by%20our%20leaders%2C%20and%20untiring%20efforts%20by%20the%20political%20leadership%2C%20military%20leaders%2C%20and%20diplomatic%20colleagues%2C%20who%20maintained%20communications%20throughout%20this%20time%2C%20our%20two%20countries%20have%20resolved%20several%20issues%20along%20the%20border%20areas.%20This%20too%2C%20holds%20a%20lesson%20for%20us%20(China%20and%20India)%20-%20which%20is%20that%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20smooth%20development%20of%20our%20overall%20bilateral%20relations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20this%20fundamental%20understanding%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20in%20the%20meeting%20between%20PM%20Modi%20and%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20in%20Russia%2C%20that%20both%20nations%20are%20now%20working%20together%20to%20chart%20a%20roadmap%20for%20our%20bilateral%20relations%2C%20to%20return%20to%20a%20stable%2C%20predictable%2C%20and%20amicable%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESharing%20specifics%20about%20the%20efforts%20made%20at%20the%20political%2C%20military%2C%20and%20diplomatic%20levels%2C%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20highlighted%20that%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%205%20months%2C%20we%20have%20had%20two%20meetings%20between%20the%20foreign%20ministers%20-%20in%20November%2C%202024%20and%20February%202025.%20Our%20Special%20Representatives%20(SRs)%20for%20the%20India-China%20boundary%20question%20met%20in%20Beijing%20in%20December%2C%202024%20for%20the%2023rd%20round%20of%20SR-level%20talks.%20After%20a%20gap%20of%20nearly%20five%20years%2C%20our%20Defence%20Minister%20met%20with%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20in%20November%2C%202024%2C%20and%20I%20(foreign%20secretary)%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20visit%20Beijing%20in%20January%2C%202025%20and%20had%20a%20very%20productive%20meeting%20with%20my%20counterpart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20and%20China%2C%20he%20said%2C%20have%20decided%20to%20take%20several%20steps%20to%20%26quot%3Bresume%20practical%20cooperation%20between%20our%20two%20countries.%20Amongst%20the%20first%20of%20these%2C%20is%20the%20resumption%20of%20the%20Kailash-Mansarovar%20yatra%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20discussing%20the%20resumption%20of%20cooperation%20on%20transport%20and%20rivers%2C%20and%20on%20direct%20air%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20noted%20that%20these%20steps%20are%20important%20and%20foremost%20in%20order%20to%20restore%20mutual%20trust%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20and%20enhance%20people-to-people%20ties.%20Highlighting%20the%20responsibility%20that%20the%20two%20major%20economies%20must%20live%20up%20to%2C%20Mr%20Misri%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20two%20large%20neighbours%20in%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20world%2C%20a%20stable%20bilateral%20relationship%20between%20our%20nations%20will%20contribute%20to%20humanity%20as%20a%20whole.%20Let%20us%20take%20this%2075th%20year%20milestone%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20rebuild%20our%20ties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBefore%20concluding%20his%20speech%2C%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20spoke%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bthird%20lesson%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20nations%20to%20keep%20in%20mind.%20%26quot%3BThe%20durable%20basis%20for%20rebuilding%20our%20ties%20is%20the%20three-fold%20formula%20of%20mutual%20respect%2C%20mutual%20sensitivity%2C%20and%20mutual%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20his%20closing%20remarks%2C%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20acknowledged%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20path%20forward%20may%20be%20a%20difficult%20one%2C%20but%20one%20that%20we%20are%20prepared%20for%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20these%20steps%20that%20we%20have%20already%20taken%20in%20the%20last%20five%20months%2C%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20promising%20beginnings%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20end%20of%20seven-and-a-half%20decades.%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20should%20now%20be%20%26quot%3Bturned%20into%20tangible%20benefit%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20people%20of%20our%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743540180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fnfd8fqlc_india-china-ladakh-generic-ndtv-fil-photo_625x300_25_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-talks-of-lessons-for-both-to-remember-as-ties-with-china-turn-75-8064929%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20China-India%20ties%20completed%2075%20years%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20India's%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20spoke%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Blessons%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20nations%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20as%20they%20work%20on%20new%20and%20promising%20beginnings%20at%20the%20end%20of%20seven-and-a-half%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20a%20terrorist%20killed%208%20people%2C%20a%20NY%20jury%20did%20not%20vote%20to%20execute%20him.%20Luigi%20Mangione's%20odds%20of%20dodging%20death%20are%20better%20yet.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luigi%20Mangione%20(left)%20and%20Sayfullo%20Saipov%20(right)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec4e5ab8b41a9673fc58a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELuigi%20Manigone%20has%20a%20good%20chance%20of%20dodging%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20ex-prosecutors%20say.%20A%20NY%20jury%20didn't%20hand%20down%20a%20death%20penalty%20to%20Sayfullo%20Saipov%2C%20who%20killed%20eight%20people.%20%3Cp%3ECurtis%20Means%2FAP%20Photo%3B%20St.%20Charles%20County%20Department%20of%20Corrections%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20seeks%20to%20execute%20Luigi%20Mangione%20for%20the%20ambush%20murder%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20government's%20odds%20for%20success%20are%20steep%2C%20given%20the%20hesitancy%20of%20death%20penalty%20juries%20in%20NY.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202023%2C%20a%20death%20penalty%20jury%20could%20not%20agree%20on%20Sayfullo%20Saipov%2C%20a%20terrorist%20who%20killed%208%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Halloween%20in%202017%2C%20an%20avowed%20Islamist%20extremist%20named%20Sayfullo%20Saipov%20drove%20a%20rental%20truck%20across%20the%20George%20Washington%20Bridge%20into%20Manhattan%2C%20then%20careened%20south%20along%20a%20popular%20west-side%20bike%20path%2C%20sending%20cyclists%20flying.%20Eight%20people%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Saipov's%20jury%20failed%20to%20send%20him%20to%20death%20row%2C%20there's%20no%20way%20another%20jury%20%E2%80%94%20sitting%2C%20like%20Saipov's%2C%20in%20a%20federal%20courtroom%20in%20Manhattan%20%E2%80%94%20will%20vote%20to%20end%20the%20life%20of%20Luigi%20Mangione%2C%20former%20federal%20prosecutors%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%20I%20don't%20believe%20any%20Manhattan%20jury%20is%20going%20to%20decide%20to%20impose%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ephraim%20Savitt%2C%20a%20former%20federal%20prosecutor%20now%20in%20private%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20does%20not%20fit%20the%20profile%20of%20a%20death%20penalty%20eligible%20criminal%2C%20he%20said%2C%20speaking%20Tuesday%20after%20Attorney%20General%20Pam%20Bondi%20said%20the%20government%20will%20seek%20the%20ultimate%20penalty%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bcold-blooded%20assassination%26quot%3B%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluigi-mangione-pam-bondi-death-penalty-murder-case-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20in%20Texas%2C%26quot%3B%20Savitt%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20not%20a%20mass%20shooting.%20It's%20not%20an%20act%20of%20terrorism.%20It's%20a%20horrible%20crime%2C%20of%20course.%20But%20as%20serious%20as%20it%20is%2C%20it%20does%20not%20fit%20in%20the%20rubric%20of%20someone%20who%20should%20be%20put%20to%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BMangione%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20sentenced%20to%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20is%20facing%20charges%20in%20three%20jurisdictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20least%20serious%20are%20the%20weapons%20and%20forgery%20charges%20out%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20where%20the%2026-year-old%20software%20developer%20from%20Maryland%20was%20arrested%20after%20a%20five-day%20manhunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20facing%20state-level%20charges%20of%20murder%20as%20an%20act%20of%20terror%20out%20of%20Manhattan%2C%20where%20DA%20Alvin%20Bragg%20has%20said%20that%20Mangione%20would%20be%20tried%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione's%20federal%20jury%20would%20be%20chosen%20from%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%2C%20which%20includes%20people%20from%20Manhattan%2C%20the%20Bronx%2C%20Westchester%20County%2C%20and%20five%20other%20counties%20on%20the%20southern%20end%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20federal%20court%2C%20now%20that%20this%20is%20an%20official%20death%20penalty%20case%2C%20a%20single%20trial%20jury%20would%20preside%20over%20a%20phase%20to%20determine%20Mangione's%20guilt%20and%20then%20another%20to%20determine%20how%20he%20should%20be%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de315f31-7338-44a5-92c5-d5e250ede040%5C%22%3EThere's%20a%20strategy%20in%20seeking%20the%20death%20penalty%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20would%20be%20comprised%20only%20of%20people%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20impose%20a%20death%20penalty%2C%20tilting%20it%20in%20the%20government's%20favor%2C%20Ephraim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20improves%20your%20odds%20of%20a%20conviction%2C%20absolutely%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Savitt%2C%20of%20the%20Ephraim%20Savitt%20Law%20Firm%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%20two%20key%20strategic%20benefits%20to%20seeking%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20former%20prosecutors%20said%2C%20even%20if%20an%20ultimate%20verdict%20of%20death%20may%20be%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20strategic%20benefit%20to%20seeking%20the%20death%20penalty%20is%20it%20gives%20the%20government%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20leverage%26quot%3B%20in%20plea%20negotiations%2C%20said%20another%20former%20federal%20prosecutor%2C%20Michael%20Bachner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20the%20defense%20lawyer%20you%20may%20want%20to%20work%20it%20out%20as%20a%20package%20%E2%80%94%20he%20pleads%20to%20both%20cases%20and%20there's%20no%20death%20penalty%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bachner%2C%20now%20in%20private%20practice%20at%20Bachner%20%26amp%3B%20Associates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Mangione's%20favor%20is%20that%20a%20death%20penalty%20verdict%20must%20be%20unanimous.%20The%20defense%20need%20only%