0him%20of%20bullying%20and%20harassment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgrindell%40businessinsider.com%20(Samantha%20Grindell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprince-harry-sentebale-chair-bullying-accusations-resignation-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20same%20badge-scan%20strategy%20used%20in%20Tesla%20layoffs%20has%20hit%20federal%20workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22HHS%20building%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec215369253ccddf9ae6fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKayla%20Bartkowski%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDOGE's%20next%20round%20of%20federal%20job%20cuts%20swept%20health%20agencies%20on%20Tuesday%20with%20plans%20to%20cut%2010%2C000%20workers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHHS%20employees%20waited%20in%20long%20lines%20to%20scan%20their%20badges%20at%20security%20to%20find%20out%20if%20they%20still%20had%20a%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20badge%20scans%20appear%20to%20be%20similar%20to%20Tesla%20layoffs%20in%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20showed%20up%20to%20their%20offices%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20learn%20their%20fate%3A%20If%20their%20badges%20worked%2C%20they%20still%20had%20a%20job.%20If%20they%20didn't%2C%20they%20had%20to%20clean%20out%20their%20desks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20crying%20the%20entire%20drive%20to%20work%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20HHS%20employee%20told%20Business%20Insider%20as%20they%20waited%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20said%20they%20saw%20a%20man%20walk%20past%2C%20wheeling%20out%20his%20personal%20belongings%20on%20a%20desk%20chair%20after%20being%20terminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20three%20people%20who%20went%20in%2C%20and%20then%20came%20back%20out%20and%20left%20with%20tears%20in%20their%20eyes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20employee%2C%20who%20was%20eventually%20let%20into%20the%20building.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20behind%20me%20are%20sniffling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20badge-swiping%20tactic%20appeared%20similar%20to%20one%20used%20by%20Tesla%2C%20the%20electric-vehicle%20maker%20helmed%20by%20DOGE's%20de%20facto%20head%2C%20Elon%20Musk.%20In%202024%2C%20some%20employees%20told%20BI%20they%20arrived%20at%20work%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-factory-workers-discover-laid-off-security-badge-scans-sources-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscovered%20they%20had%20been%20axed%20when%20their%20badges%20failed%20to%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HHS%20firings%20are%20part%20of%20DOGE%20and%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20goal%20to%20reduce%20government%20waste%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-federal-workers-appeal-firings-layoffs-lawsuits-trump-probationary-unions-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslash%20the%20federal%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20March%2027%2C%20Health%20Secretary%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20announced%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-slashing-10-000-jobs-at-hhs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterminate%20about%2010%2C000%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3BHHS%20is%20a%20sprawling%20bureaucracy%20that%20encompasses%20literally%20hundreds%20of%20departments%2C%20committees%2C%20and%20other%20offices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20leads%20to%20tremendous%20waste%20and%20duplication%2C%20and%20worst%20of%20all%2C%20a%20loss%20of%20any%20unified%20sense%20of%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHHS%20is%20responsible%20for%20a%20range%20of%20key%20health%20programs%20and%20agenc