by%20the%20government.%20The%20bank%20has%20approved%20advance%20tenders%20for%20the%20project%20and%20initial%20processes%20have%20been%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20operational%2C%20the%20ropeway%20will%20provide%20a%20seamless%2C%20panoramic%20travel%20experience%20while%20significantly%20reducing%20vehicular%20congestion%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20expected%20to%20revolutionise%20Shimla's%20transportation%20system%20by%20offering%20a%20modern%2C%20eco-friendly%20alternative%20that%20will%20enhance%20connectivity%2C%20improve%20air%20quality%20and%20boost%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20longest%20ropeway%20in%20the%20world%20is%20in%20Bolivia%2C%20spanning%20approximately%2032%20kilometers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743533160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fes40qt18_shimla-ropeway-project_625x300_01_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshimla-builds-asias-longest-ropeway-to-ferry-2-000-people-every-hour-8063398%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shima%20is%20set%20to%20construct%20the%20world's%20second-longest%20ropeway%20project%2C%20spanning%2013.79%20kilometers%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20boost%20tourism%20and%20alleviate%20traffic%20congestion%20in%20the%20popular%20hill%20station.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshimla-builds-asias-longest-ropeway-to-ferry-2-000-people-every-hour-8063398%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Hikes%20Tax%20On%20Diesel%2C%20Price%20Rises%20By%20Rs%202%20Per%20Litre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20government%20has%20hiked%20the%20sales%20tax%20on%20diesel%20to%2021.17%20per%20cent%20with%20effect%20from%20Tuesday%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20there%20will%20be%20an%20increase%20of%20Rs%202%20per%20litre%2C%20bringing%20the%20sale%20price%20to%20Rs%2091.02.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20statement%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Karnataka%20Sales%20Tax%20rate%20on%20diesel%20was%20at%2024%20per%20cent%20prior%20to%20November%204%2C%202021%2C%20and%20the%20sale%20price%20per%20litre%20was%20Rs%2092.03.%20On%20June%2015%2C%202024%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20state%20government%20issued%20a%20notification%20revising%20the%20tax%20rate%20on%20diesel%20to%2018.44%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Competent%20Authority%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20Sales%20Tax%20rate%20on%20diesel%20has%20been%20increased%20to%2021.17%20per%20cent%2C%20effective%20from%2001-04-2025.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20will%20be%20an%20increase%20of%20Rs%202%20per%20litre%2C%20bringing%20the%20sale%20price%20to%20Rs%2091.02%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20after%20this%20increase%2C%20the%20revised%20sales%20price%20in%20the%20state%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20lower%20compared%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20states%2C%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20on%20March%2031%2C%202025%2C%20the%20diesel%20price%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20Rs%2089.02%2C%20whereas%20in%20Hosur%20(Tamil%20Nadu)%20it%20is%20Rs%2094.42%2C%20Kasaragod%20(Kerala)%20Rs%2095.66%2C%20Anathapura%20(Andhra%20Pradesh)%20Rs%2097.35%2C%20Hyderabad%20(Telangana)%20Rs%2095.70%20and%20Kagal%20(Maharashtra)%20Rs%2091.07%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20move%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20Assembly%2C%20R%20Ashoka%2C%20accused%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20of%20imposing%20taxes%20on%20items%20one%20by%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20the%20state%20government%20was%20increasing%20prices%20and%20%26quot%3Bsucking%20blood%20of%20poor%20and%20middle%20class%20people.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20post%20on%20%26quot%3BX%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20poor%20%40INCKarnaraka%20government%20has%20increased%20the%20price%20of%20milk%2C%20imposed%20a%20cess%20on%20garbage%20collection%2C%20and%20now%20it%20has%20suddenly%20increased%20the%20price%20of%20diesel%20by%20Rs%202%20per%20litre.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDiesel%20is%20the%20fuel%20used%20for%20transporting%20goods.%20Doesn't%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20a%20self-proclaimed%20economist%2C%20know%20that%20if%20the%20price%20of%20diesel%20increases%2C%20the%20prices%20of%20all%20essential%20goods%20and%20services%2C%20including%20milk%2C%20vegetables%2C%20fruits%2C%20groceries%2C%20taxis%2C%20will%20increase%3F%20Bus%20ticket%20prices%20were%20recently%20increased%20without%20money%20to%20pay%20salaries%20to%20transport%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20bus%20ticket%20prices%20will%20be%20increased%20again%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20diesel%20price%20hike.%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20have%20you%20been%20wondering%20which%20items%20should%20be%20taxed%20and%20which%20items%20should%20be%20increased%20in%20price%3F%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743532800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fcu89i0qg_petrol-diesel-generic-fuel-generic-ani_625x300_29_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-government-hikes-diesel-tax-price-rises-by-rs-2-per-litre-8064504%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka%20government%20has%20hiked%20the%20sales%20tax%20on%20diesel%20to%2021.17%20per%20cent%20with%20effect%20from%20Tuesday%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20there%20will%20be%20an%20increase%20of%20Rs%202%20per%20litre%2C%20bringing%20the%20sale%20price%20to%20Rs%2091.02.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%