C%20as%20they%20recovered%2017%20kg%20of%20gold%20worth%20Rs%2013%20crore%20and%20arrested%20six%20people%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20accused%20was%20identified%20as%20Vijaykumar%20and%20he%20was%20assisted%20by%20Ajaykumar%20(28)%2C%20Abheesheka%20(23)%2C%20Chandru%20(23)%2C%20Manjunath%20(32)%20and%20Paramananda%20(30)%20in%20the%20heist%20that%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Nyamati%20branch%20on%20October%2028.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVijaykumar%20and%20Ajaykumar%20are%20brothers%20while%20Paramanda%20is%20the%20husband%20of%20their%20sister.%20All%20three%20are%20originally%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20but%20have%20had%20a%20sweets%20business%20in%20Nyamati%20for%20many%20years.%20The%20other%20three%20accused%2C%20Abhisheka%2C%20Chandru%20and%20Manjunath%20are%20from%20Nyamati%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReason%20Behind%20Heist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20that%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20robbery%20revealed%20that%20Vijaykumar%20was%20facing%20financial%20distress%20when%20he%20approached%20SBI%20for%20a%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20loan%20in%20August%20last%20year.%20His%20loan%20application%20was%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20by%20the%20bank%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20think%20of%20other%20means%20to%20obtain%20the%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Accused%20Planned%20Robbery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijaykumar%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20Spanish%20crime%20drama%20'Money%20Heist'%20and%20immersed%20himself%20in%20YouTube%20videos%20for%20six%20to%20nine%20months%20to%20chalk%20out%20the%20robbery%20plan%2C%20taking%20extreme%20precautions%20to%20cover%20his%20tracks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlawless%20Execution%20A%20Challenge%20For%20Cops%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijaykumar%2C%20the%20police%20said%2C%20took%20help%20from%20his%20brother%2C%20brother-in-law%20and%20three%20trusted%20associates%20for%20the%20heist.%20He%20and%20Chandru%20carried%20out%20multiple%20recce%20of%20the%20bank%20and%20held%20mock%20drills%20at%20night%2C%20through%20deserted%20fields%2C%20to%20assess%20police%20and%20civilian%20movement%2C%20and%20the%20time%20taken.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gang%20used%20equipment%20like%20silent%20hydraulic%20iron%20cutters%20and%20gas-cutting%20tools%20to%20break%20into%20the%20bank%20lockers.%20Further%2C%20the%20entry%20through%20a%20window%2C%20decamping%20with%20the%20DVR%20and%20complete%20non-usage%20of%20mobile%20phones%20left%20the%20cops%20struggling%20for%20clues%20to%20solve%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijaykumar%20even%20erased%20serial%20numbers%20from%20an%20oxygen%20cylinder%20that%20he%20used%20for%20cutting%20security%20barriers.%20The%20accused%20had%20also%20spread%20chilli%20powder%20across%20the%20premises%2C%20including%20the%20strong%20room%20and%20the%20manager's%20cabin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20gang%20had%20already%20started%20liquidating%20the%20gold%2C%20reinvesting%20in%20businesses%20and%20even%20selling%20them%20to%20use%20the%20money%20to%20buy%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fpni5n99_karnataka-heist_625x300_01_April_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProbe%20Extended%20To%20Other%20States%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20November%20to%20February%2C%20the%20investigation%20teams%20conducted%20several%20operations%20in%20difficult%20terrains%20across%20various%20states%2C%20mainly%20Gujarat%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20apprehend%20the%20accused%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20the%20gathered%20eviden