%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20have%20been%20denied%20by%20Baghel%2C%20who%20termed%20the%20CBI%20action%20as%20politically%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20registered%20the%20FIR%20on%20December%2018%20last%20year%20and%20conducted%20searches%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20Baghel%20on%20March%2026.%20The%20FIR%20was%20made%20public%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20procedure%20in%20cases%20referred%20to%20the%20CBI%20by%20a%20state%20government%2C%20the%20agency%20re-registers%20the%20FIR%20of%20the%20state%20police%20as%20its%20own%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20FIR%20as%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20the%20central%20agency%20probes%20the%20case%20and%20gives%20its%20findings%20to%20a%20special%20court%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20final%20report%2C%20which%20may%20or%20may%20not%20carry%20the%20allegations%20of%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20EOW%2C%20referred%20to%20the%20CBI%20by%20the%20state%20government%2C%20was%20filed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20report%20to%20state%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20report%2C%20which%20became%20part%20of%20the%20EOW%20FIR%20and%20now%20the%20CBI%20case%2C%20alleged%20that%20Dubai-based%20Sourabh%20Chandrakar%2C%20Ravi%20Uppal%2C%20Shubham%20Soni%2C%20and%20Anil%20Kumar%20Agrawal%20are%20the%20main%20owners%20of%20the%20company%20'Mahadev%20Online%20Book'%20which%20ran%20an%20online%20%26quot%3Bbetting%20empire%26quot%3B%20through%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20call%20centres.%26quot%3B%20The%20report%20also%20said%20that%20the%20promoters%20and%20associates%20of%20the%20company%20have%20obtained%20citizenship%20of%20Vanuatu%20in%20%26quot%3Border%20to%20escape%20the%20clutches%20of%20law.%26quot%3B%20It%20alleged%20that%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20and%20its%20sister%20concerns%20were%20generating%20betting%20proceeds%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20450%20crore%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20alleged%20that%20promoters%20and%20associates%20were%20dealing%20in%20cryptocurrencies%20to%20hide%20the%20money%20trail%20from%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20alleged%20role%20of%20Baghel%2C%20the%20ED%20report%20said%20that%20he%20has%20been%20named%20by%20the%20promoters%20of%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeneficiary%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20betting%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20also%20been%20revealed%20by%20Chandrabhushan%20Verma%20(a%20police%20personnel%20who%20was%20the%20main%20link%20between%20Dubai-based%20promoters%20and%20Chhattisgarh-based%20powers%20that%20be)%20that%20his%20(Baghel's)%20OSD%20and%20political%20advisor%20were%20being%20paid%20proceeds%20out%20of%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20regularly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%2C%20now%20part%20of%20the%20CBI%20FIR%2C%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20said%20that%20in%202023%2C%20it%20had%20seized%20Rs%205.39%20crore%20in%20cash%20from%20one%20Asim%20Das%2C%20an%20alleged%20cash%20courier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20agency%20said%20it%20was%20able%20to%20obtain%20from%20the%20mobile%20phone%20of%20Asim%20Das%20a%20voice%20note%2C%20which%20was%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20shared%20by%20Shubham%20Soni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recording%2C%20it%20alleged%2C%20made%20it%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20evident%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20seized%20account%20was%20meant%20for%20one%20%26quot%3BMr%20Baghel%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20identified%20by%20Asim%20Das%20as%20%26quot%3BEx-CM%20of%20state%20Mr%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20statement%20he%20gave%20on%20November%203%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20the%20voice%20note%2C%20it%20was%20also%20gathered%20that%20Shubham%20Soni%20was%20claiming%20that%20he%20had%20also%20made%20such%20payments%20prior%20to%20this%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20arrested%20Das%20in%202023%20from%20a%20hotel%20in%20Raipur%2C%20just%20before%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20March%2026%20searches%2C%20Baghel%20had%20said%20the%20previous%20Congress%20government%20had%20taken%20stern%20action%20against%20Mahadev%20betting%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20(previous)%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20around%2074%20FIRs%20were%20lodged%20in%20connection%20with%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20and%20more%20than%20200%20people%20were%20arrested%20and%20over%202%2C000%20bank%20accounts%20related%20to%20it%20were%20frozen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20action%20against%20the%20app%20but%20they%20(government%20agencies)%20claim%20we%20protected%20the%20app%20and%20took%20money.%20How%20will%20the%20one%20who%20takes%20action%20accept%20the%20protection%20money%3F%20Protection%20money%20is%20taken%20where%20there%20is%20a%20double%20engine%20(government)%20and%20betting%20is%20still%20functional%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaghel%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20then%20Congress%20government%20had%20requested%20the%20Centre%20to%20issue%20a%20lookout%20circular%20against%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal%20and%20arrest%20them%20from%20foreign%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20(religious%20guru)%20Pradeep%20Mishra%2C%20who%20praises%20BJP%2C%20visited%20Dubai%20by%20becoming%20a%20guest%20of%20Saurabh%20Chandrakar%20and%20Ravi%20Uppal.%20If%20CBI%20officials%20have%20courage%2C%20they%20should%20ask%20Pardeep%20Mishra%20whose%20programme%20is%20currently%20underway%20in%20the%20home%20district%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20in%20Jashpur%2C%20about%20his%20relations%20with%20Saurabh%20Chandrakar%20and%20Pradeep%20Mishra%2C%26quot%3B%20Baghel%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20in%20its%20statement%20after%20the%20searches%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BInvestigations%20have%20revealed%20that%20the%20promoters%20allegedly%20paid%20substantial%20amounts%20as%20'protection%20money'%20to%20public%20servants%20to%20ensure%20the%20smooth%20and%20uninterrupted%20functioning%20of%20their%20illegal%20betting%20network.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743524940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjnct110g_bhupesh-baghel_625x300_15_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhupesh-baghel-among-alleged-beneficiaries-of-mahadev-betting-scam-report-8063941%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20was%20allegedly%20one%20of%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Mahadev%20Betting%20scam%2C%20according%20to%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20report%2C%20which%20is%20now%20part%20of%20the%20CBI%20FIR%2C%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhupesh-baghel-among-alleged-beneficiaries-of-mahadev-betting-scam-report-8063941%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22German%20Tourist%20Raped%20Inside%20Car%20In%20Hyderabad%2C%20Accused%20Arrested%3A%20Police%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2022-year-old%20German%20tourist%20was%20allegedly%20raped%20by%20a%2024-year-old%20man%20inside%20a%20car%20he%20had%20taken%20on%20rent%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20police%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20rape%20and%20arrested%2C%20the%20police%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20near%20Mamidipally%20area%20in%20Pahadi%20Shareef%20region%2C%20when%20the%20survivor%20was%20travelling%20in%20the%20accused's%20car%20to%20explore%20the%20city%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Eid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rachakonda%20police%20commissioner%20Sudheer%20Babu%2C%20the%20survivor%20alleged%20she%20and%20another%20man%20from%20Germany%20arrived%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20March%204%20to%20visit%20a%20friend%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20studied%20with%20them%20in%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20woman%20and%20her%20friend%20from%20Germany%20were%20hanging%20out%20in%20Meerpet%20area%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20Eid%20celebrations%20when%20the%20accused%20arrived%20with%20four%20to%20five%20children%20in%20the%20car%2C%20and%20offered%20the%20foreigners%20a%20ride%20around%20the%20city.%20The%20woman%20and%20her%20friend%20boarded%20the%20vehicle%20and%20visited%20several%20locations%20for%20an%20hour%2C%20taking%20photographs%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Babu%20said%20that%20after%20the%20woman's%20friend%20and%20the%20children%20got%20down%20to%20take%20more%20photos%20at%20one%20point%2C%20the%20accused%20drove%20around%20100%20metres%20further%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20taking%20the%20survivor%20to%20a%20better%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20then%20threatened%20the%20woman%20inside%20the%20car%20and%20allegedly%20raped%20her%20before%20fleeing%20the%20spot%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survivor%20informed%20her%20German%20friend%2C%20following%20which%20the%20duo%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Babu%20said%20the%20accused%20had%20rented%20the%20car%20from%20an%20app-based%20service%20provider%20for%20a%20long%20drive%20with%20the%20children%20living%20in%20his%20locality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%2C%20along%20with%20the%20children%20and%20foreigners%2C%20had%20visited%20a%20fuel%20pump%20station%20during%20the%20course%20of%20the%20ride.%20A%20receipt%20obtained%20from%20the%20fuel%20pump%20station%20helped%20the%20cops%20to%20catch%20the%20culprit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20and%20a%20detaile