Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWatch%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Watch%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20Claims%20He%20%26quot%3BHeard%20India%20Will%20Drop%20Tariffs%20Substantially%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fu1zdyh97Lk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fu1zdyh97Lk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NDTV%20WORLD%20(%40NDTVWORLD)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNDTVWORLD%2Fstatus%2F1907074657444098206%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%201%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20however%2C%20did%20not%20give%20any%20names%20or%20specifics%20which%20back%20his%20claim%20that%20India%20will%20be%20significantly%20reducing%20tariffs%2C%20which%20have%20been%20in%20place%20for%20decades.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20official%20confirmation%20on%20the%20matter%20by%20India%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20also%20denied%20that%20his%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20might%20push%20allies%20and%20partners%20more%20towards%20China.%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20it%20won't%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20US%20President%20bluntly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20GEARS%20UP%20FOR%20'LIBERATION%20DAY'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20US%20have%20been%20negotiating%20on%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%20trade%20deal%20even%20amid%20repeated%20threats%20of%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20by%20the%20Trump%20Administration.%20The%20US%20President%20has%20called%20April%202%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20countries%20will%20drop%20its%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20fearing%20America's%20move%20to%20do%20to%20them%2C%20as%20they%20do%20to%20us%2C%20claimed%20Mr%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20number%20of%20occasions%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20labelled%20India%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Btariff%20king%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20said%20that%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20%26quot%3Babuser%20of%20tariffs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20White%20House%20Press%20Secretary%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20spoke%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20trade%20practices%20in%20India's%20tariff%20structure%2C%20highlighting%20how%20India%20imposes%20100%20per%20cent%20tariffs%20on%20agricultural%20imports%20from%20the%20US.%20She%20also%20mentioned%20similar%20high%20tariff%20structures%20by%20the%20EU%20(50%20per%20cent%20on%20American%20dairy%20products)%2C%20Japan%20(700%20per%20cent%20on%20rice)%2C%20and%20Canada%20(300%20per%20cent%20on%20butter%20and%20cheese).%20These%20hinder%20and%20hurt%20US%20exports%20and%20leads%20to%20imbalances%20and%20trade%20deficits%20in%20the%20US%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20makes%20it%20virtually%20impossible%20for%20American%20products%20to%20be%20imported%20into%20these%20markets%2C%20and%20it%20puts%20a%20lot%20of%20Americans%20out%20of%20business%20and%20out%20of%20work%20over%20the%20past%20several%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESTEPS%20TAKEN%20BY%20INDIA%20SO%20FAR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20countries%20have%20vowed%20to%20retaliate%20US%20reciprocal%20tariffs%2C%20India%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20countries%20which%20wants%20to%20avoid%20animosity%20and%20friction%2C%20and%20has%20hence%20been%20working%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20manage%20the%20India-US%20trade%20ties%20amicably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20already%20reduced%20tariffs%20on%20certain%20products%20like%20Harley%20Davidson%20motorbikes%20and%20American%20bourbon%20whiskey.%20According%20to%20a%20Reuters%20report%2C%20India%20has%20apparently%20also%20offered%20to%20reduce%20import%20duties%20on%20select%20agricultural%20products.%20News%20agency%20Reuters%20also%20claims%20that%20India%20has%20offered%20reductions%20on%20more%20than%20half%20of%20US%20imports%20worth%20%2423%20billion%20-%20but%20only%20if%20US%20exempts%20India%20from%20any%20reciprocal%20tariff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20annual%20Union%20Budget%20for%202025%2C%20India%20has%20already%20announced%20reduction%20of%20customs%20duties%20on%20American%20solar%20cells%2C%20machinery%2C%20and%20luxury%20cars.%20India%20has%20also%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20remove%20the%206%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20digital%20advertisements%20starting%20April%201%2C%202025%20-%20a%20move%20that%20will%20greatly%20benefit%20US%20tech%20firms%20like%20Meta%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20US%20also%20aim%20to%20speed%20up%20talks%20of%20a%20mega%20trade%20deal%20much%20before%20its%20autumn%20deadline.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743520740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Ffr2uug4k_donald-trump-oval-office-afp_625x300_01_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-donald-trump-claims-he-heard-india-will-drop-tariffs-substantially-8063484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Little%20over%20twenty-four%20hours%20before%20he%20drops%20the%20reciprocal%20tariff%20bomb%20for%20the%20world%2C%20including%20his%20countrymen%20to%20deal%20with%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20made%20a%20stunning%20claim%20-%20that%20he%20heard%20India%20will%20drop%20tariffs%20on%20US%20imports%20substantially.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-donald-trump-claims-he-heard-india-will-drop-tariffs-substantially-8063484%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Court%20Rejects%20Claim%20Of%20Summons%20Being%20Served%20On%20Ajit%20Doval%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20US%20court%20has%20said%20that%20no%20complaint%20was%20delivered%20to%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Washington%20in%20February%2C%20dismissing%20a%20claim%20by%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20that%20court