ock%20of%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20labourer%2C%20whose%20wife%20is%20suffering%20from%20tuberculosis%2C%20has%20received%20a%20notice%20from%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20stating%20that%20he%20owes%20them%20over%20Rs%2011%20crore%20in%20outstanding%20taxes.%20And%20he%20is%20one%20of%20three%20such%20people%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20district%20-%20the%20others%20being%20a%20juice%20vendor%20and%20a%20cleaner%20-%20who%20have%20been%20sent%20similar%20notices%20in%20the%20past%20fortnight%20alone%2C%20prompting%20speculation%20that%20their%20Aadhaar%20and%20PAN%20cards%20may%20have%20been%20misused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20in%20front%20of%20his%20house%2C%20which%20was%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20Yogesh%20Sharma%2C%20who%20works%20at%20a%20factory%20that%20manufactures%20springs%20used%20for%20locks%2C%20said%20his%20family's%20financial%20situation%20was%20already%20abysmal%20and%20they%20were%20so%20shocked%20after%20getting%20the%20notice%20that%20and%20he%20his%20wife%20skipped%20multiple%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20notice%20is%20dated%20March%2020%20and%20says%20that%20I%20owe%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20Rs%2011.12%20crore%20(Rs%2011%2C11%2C85%2C991).%20I%20have%20never%20even%20heard%20of%20such%20an%20amount%2C%20much%20less%20seen%20it.%20My%20wife%20and%20I%20haven't%20eaten%20since%20we%20got%20the%20notice.%20I%20live%20on%20rent%20and%20the%20electricity%20has%20been%20cut%20since%20a%20week%20because%20I%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20pay%20the%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20has%20TB%20and%20she%20has%20been%20undergoing%20treatment.%20Everyone%20in%20the%20family%20is%20worried%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaran%20Kumar%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20cleaner%20on%20contract%20with%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20earns%20Rs%2015%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20received%20an%20Income%20Tax%20notice%20of%20Rs%2033.89%20crore%20(33%2C8