20declared%2C%20speaking%20after%20a%20Comptroller%20%26amp%3B%20Auditor-General%20report%20-%20that%20audited%20the%20AAP's%20battle%20against%20air%20pollution%20-%20was%20tabled%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Rekha%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20these%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20highlighted%20failures%20of%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20controlling%20vehicular%20emission%2C%20such%20as%20not%20keeping%20data%20about%20the%20type%20and%20number%20of%20vehicles%20plying%20on%20Delhi%20roads%20and%20assessment%20of%20emission%20loads.%20It%20also%20flagged%20a%20shortage%20of%20buses%20and%20other%20options%20that%20would%20allow%20commuters%20to%20overcome%20last-mile%20connectivity%20issues%20and%20use%20public%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sirsa%20later%20told%20reporters%20the%20Delhi%20government%20at%20the%20time%20had%20been%20told%20of%20the%20need%20for%2011%2C000%20buses%20but%2C%20instead%2C%20fleet%20size%20was%20reduced%20by%20more%20than%2020%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20also%20red-flagged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20issue%20of%20PUC%20(pollution%20under%20control)%20certificates%20for%20vehicles%2C%20unreliable%20air%20quality%20monitors%2C%20and%20poor%20enforcement%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20PUC%20issue%2C%20the%20report%20said%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20multiple%20vehicles%20were%20issued%20certificates%20from%20the%20same%20testing%20centre%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20sometimes%20within%20a%20minute%20of%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20should%20not%20be%20possible%20since%20each%20pollution%20test%20can%20take%20several%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20between%202015%20and%202020%2C%20nearly%204%2C000%20diesel%20vehicles%20were%20found%20to%20have%20exceeded%20emission%20norms%20but%20were%20still%20certified%20as%20'compliant'%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20CAG%20report%20further%20said%2C%20also%20lacked%20data%20about%20the%20number%2C%20type%2C%20and%20emission%20loads%20of%20vehicles%20on%20city%20roads%2C%20which%20meant%20it%20could%20not%20come%20up%20with%20source-specific%20plans%20to%20tackle%20what%20is%20an%20annual%20and%20dangerous%20air%20quality%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVehicular%20emissions%20are%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20contributors%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20air%20pollution%20crisis%2C%20the%20CAG%20report%20said%2C%20noting%20also%20the%20lack%20of%20data%20about%20benzene%20levels%2C%20or%20means%20to%20reduce%20these%2C%20at%20fuel%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20pointed%20to%20a%20number%20of%20other%20concerns%2C%20including%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Pollution%20Control%20Committee%20to%20record%20data%20for%20as%20many%20as%2016%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20including%20of%20lead%20in%20the%20air%20and%20real-time%20information%20about%20sources%20of%20pollutants%2C%20leading%20to%20skewed%20final%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20pressing%20need%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20now%20take%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20steps%20to%20address%20gaps%20in%20air%20quality%20monitoring%20and%20vehicular%20emission%20control%20measures%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20CAG%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20is%20one%20of%2014%20the%20new%20BJP%20government%20has%20said%20will%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20as%20part%20of%20an%20'audit'%20of%20the%20previous%20administration.%20Eight%2C%20including%20a%20report%20on%20the%20liquor%20excise%20policy%20scam%20that%20roiled%20the%20AAP%20before%20the%20February%20election%2C%20have%20been%20tabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20returned%20to%20power%20in%20Delhi%20in%20style%2C%20winning%2048%20of%20the%20city's%2070%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20election.%20The%20AAP%2C%20which%20had%20won%20over%2060%20in%20eac