out%20taking%20a%20punch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040-year-old%20boxer%20received%20first%20aid%20in%20the%20ring%20before%20being%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20pronounced%20dead%2030%20minutes%20after%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ghana%20Boxing%20Authority%20(GBA)%2C%20Oluwasegun%20Olanrewaju%20stepped%20back%20and%20leaned%20against%20the%20ropes%20just%20seconds%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20third%20round%2C%20without%20taking%20a%20punch%20from%20his%20opponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensing%20distress%2C%20the%20referee%20stopped%20the%20fight%20and%20called%20for%20the%20ringside%20physician%2C%20who%2C%20along%20with%20paramedics%20from%20the%20National%20Ambulance%20Service%2C%20attempted%20to%20resuscitate%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GBA%20stated%20that%20Olanrewaju%20had%20been%20declared%20medically%20fit%20by%20the%20Nigeria%20Boxing%20Board%20Control%20(NBBC)%2C%20which%20had%20sanctioned%20and%20approved%20the%20fight.%20However%2C%20the%20NBBC%20later%20told%20The%20Punch%20that%20it%20had%20not%20authorized%20the%20specific%20bout%20in%20which%20he%20passed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Olanrewaju%20was%20initially%20scheduled%20to%20fight%20on%20Friday%20but%20was%20deemed%20overweight%20for%20the%20match.%20NBBC%20secretary%20Remi%20Aboderin%20told%20The%20Punch%20that%20after%20failing%20the%20weigh-in%2C%20the%20boxer%20attempted%20to%20return%20to%20Nigeria%20but%20later%20decided%20to%20stay%20in%20Ghana%20due%20to%20financial%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20owed%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Aboderin%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20matchmaker%20informed%20him%20of%20another%20fight%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20but%20we%20did%20not%20approve%20that%20bout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAboderin%20described%20Olanrewaju%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bring%20warrior%26quot%3B%20and%20expressed%20the%20federation's%20deep%20sorrow%20over