ood%20swings%2C%20mental%20breakdowns%2C%20and%20irregular%20periods.%20Studying%20for%20a%20BTech%20degree%20while%20living%20alone%20in%20Indore%2C%20she%20was%20under%20constant%20stress%2C%20juggling%20academics%2C%20sleepless%20nights%2C%20and%20the%20overwhelming%20frustration%20of%20not%20knowing%20why%20her%20body%20was%20failing%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESpotting%20PCOS%20early%20%E2%80%93%20an%20expert%20breaks%20down%20the%20symptoms%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nidhi%20Tripathi%2C%20a%20gynaecologist%20and%20fertility%20specialist%20at%20Birla%20Fertility%20%26amp%3B%20IVF%2C%20Noida%2C%20with%20over%2012%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20explains%20the%20complexities%20of%20Polycystic%20Ovary%20Syndrome%20(PCOS)%2C%20emphasising%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20hormonal%20problem%20that%20can%20arise%20due%20to%20environmental%20factors%20or%20genetics.%20For%20many%20women%2C%20the%20first%20sign%20of%20PCOS%20is%20irregular%20menstruation.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC0346-1_11zon-1743132058-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Greek%20yoghurt%20became%20a%20staple%20diet%20for%20Harshita%2C%20when%20she%20wanted%20to%20curb%20her%20cravings%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC0346-1_11zon-1743132058-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC0346-1_11zon-1743132058-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC0346-1_11zon-1743132058-768x960.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC0346-1_11zon-1743132058-1228x1536.jpg%201228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F