nd_11zon-1743077050-500x257.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FShiv-Kumar-Green-Entrepreneur-LED-bulb-manufacturer-Dadda-Patti-Uttarakhand_11zon-1743077050-768x395.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FShiv-Kumar-Green-Entrepreneur-LED-bulb-manufacturer-Dadda-Patti-Uttarakhand_11zon-1743077050-1536x790.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FShiv-Kumar-Green-Entrepreneur-LED-bulb-manufacturer-Dadda-Patti-Uttarakhand_11zon-1743077050-1200x617.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FShiv-Kumar-Green-Entrepreneur-LED-bulb-manufacturer-Dadda-Patti-Uttarakhand_11zon-1743077050-150x77.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-416328%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22987%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGreen%20entrepreneur%20Shiv%20Kumar%20is%20an%20LED%20bulb%20manufacturer%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20social%20enterprise%2C%20%E2%80%98Development%20Alternatives%E2%80%99%2C%20launched%20the%20%E2%80%98Inclusive%20Entrepreneurship%E2%80%99%20programme%20with%20one%20big%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20turning%20job%20seekers%20into%20job%20creators.%20Instead%20of%20focusing%20solely%20on%20providing%20jobs%2C%20the%20programme%20set%20out%20to%20build%20entrepreneurial%20ecosystems%20%E2%80%94%20support%20systems%20that%20help%20people%20start%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F113935%2Ffoundation-poor-women-business-owners-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20their%20own%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20vision%20aimed%20at%20underserved%20communities%2C%20particularly%20women%20and%20youth%20and%20seeks%20to%20create%20long-term%20economic%20growth%20while%20promoting%20social%20inclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20unique%20approach%20rooted%20in%20social%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20reduce%20entrepreneurship%20to%20clich%C3%A9s%20instead%20of%20building%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20view.%20Inclusive%20entrepreneurship%20is%20about%20creating%20an%20economy%20where%20millions%20of%20%E2%80%98job%20seekers%E2%80%99%20become%20%E2%80%98job%20makers%E2%80%99%20in%20their%20communities%20while%20prioritising%20social%20inclusion%2C%20environmental%20sustainability%2C%20and%20economic%20growth.%20By%20bridging%20skill%20gaps%2C%20co-creating%20with%20communities%2C%20and%20enabling%20entrepreneurial%20ecosystems%2C%20we%20can%20drive%20innovation%2C%20scale%20businesses%2C%20and%20lower%20the%20costs%20of%20setting%20up%20enterprises.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20Shrashtant%20Patara%2C%20CEO%2C%20Development%20Alternatives%20Group.%20These%20words%20make%20it%20evident%20what%20sets%20the%20Inclusive%20Entrepreneurship%20programme%20apart%20%E2%80%94%20an%20innovative%2C%20community-driven%20approach.%20The%20idea%20is%20simple%20yet%20profound%3A%20wisdom%20and%20solutions%20lie%20within%20the%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20aspects%20of%20this%20approach%20is%20something%20called%20%E2%80%98deep%20listening%E2%80%99.%20This%20means%20immersing%20fully%20in%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20world%20%E2%80%94%20understanding%20their%20culture%2C%20challenges%2C%20and%20aspirations%20%E2%80%94%20while%20making%20careful%20observations.%20The%20programme%20combines%20deep%20listening%20with%20steps%20like%20%E2%80%9Cco-creation%E2%80%9D%2C%20where%20solutions%20are%20developed%20together%20with%20the%20participants%2C%20%E2%80%9Cprototyping%E2%80%9D%20to%20test%20ideas%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cacceleration%E2%80%9D%20to%20bring%20these%20ideas%20to%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%